2.2.0 - 2017-04-16
------------------------------------------------------------
* CLI now downloads & extracts source from Github instead of bundling with the kit
* Adds ESLint and `npm run lint` step
* Removes redundant `klaw` and `through2` packages

2.1.2 - 2017-04-15
------------------------------------------------------------
